reviewText: Straight-arrow mayor tries to clean up politically corrupt city. Things don't go well. This is a primitive Precode with amateurish acting and a clunky screen play, but with a little Precode naughtiness, a spunky leading lady, and a decent story, this film is actually entertaining.
